{"tid":224370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【提提你】今日起搭九巴95折 為期2個月","createTime":"2017-05-01T04:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T07:30:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b791ae43e5a491ba9d82d1b5a6185512a1dd946","tid":224370,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T04:19:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170501&amp;guid=56612373&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170501%26guid%3D56612373%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=754c0ab0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170501%26guid%3D56612373%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=f79abd05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170501&amp;guid=56612373&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n即時要聞  2017-05-01 05:00:47 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n九巴及龍運公司今年不會加價，今年5月1日起，所有獨營路線以八達通繳付成人票價的乘客，均可獲95折優惠，並可與現時巴士轉乘優惠同時使用，優惠期兩個月。九巴今次回饋乘客計劃，不包括K12、K14、K17及K18路線。<br />\n<br />\n九巴去年錄得除稅後盈利6.177億元，較前年增加1.295億元，龍運巴士則去年錄得可除稅後盈利3,120萬元，較前年減少2,580萬元。九巴的的乘客回饋計劃，是根據九巴與政府的協議，回報率若超過按其固定資產平均淨值計算的指定觸發回報率，其高於指定觸發回報率的50%會與乘客分享，以紓緩日後車費加價壓力，及向乘客提供車費優惠。"},{"pid":"4c56b11ffcb7b0b49bf4b73359411c607ed9a904","tid":224370,"uid":93629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170501&amp;guid=56612373&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170501%26guid%3D56612373%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=754c0ab0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170501%26guid%3D56612373%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=f79abd05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170501&amp;guid=56612373&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n即時要聞  2017-05-01 05:00:47 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n九巴及龍運公司今年不會加價，今年5月1日起，所有獨營路線以八達通繳付成人票價的乘客，均可獲95折優惠，並可與現時巴士轉乘優惠同時使用，優惠期兩個月。九巴今次回饋乘客計劃，不包括K12、K14、K17及K18路線。<br />\n<br />\n九巴去年錄得除稅後盈利6.177億元，較前年增加1.295億元，龍運巴士則去年錄得可除稅後盈利3,120萬元，較前年減少2,580萬元。九巴的的乘客回饋計劃，是根據九巴與政府的協議，回報率若超過按其固定資產平均淨值計算的指定觸發回報率，其高於指定觸發回報率的50%會與乘客分享，<strong>以紓緩日後車費加價壓力</strong>，及向乘客提供車費優惠。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到尾都係要加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e026babc4b179e3fb9ab3342fbaa0e92ed56ac","tid":224370,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T04:44:25.000Z","msg":"今朝搭234x都係收左我8.9喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de489b955edd37afde4c61b4036d9deac6e131de","tid":224370,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T05:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6e3f0301e47dc06cbbffe79514661e56375c38","tid":224370,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ce6559cda873c2b5e33939cfb03cfb58dcadfe","tid":224370,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:30:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}